defaultThis Council is of the view that support, care or supervision elements of the exempt accommodation definition are met by the activities undertaken in the Council’s owned hostels
default (used for statutory homeless placements)
default. 
defaultHowever, the exclusion of district councils within the exempt accommodation definition means that these hostels will not be exempt under Universal Credit (UC).
